data.description: Welcome home to 5106 Greenbrach Street. This home is situated on just over 2.5 private acres and features four bedrooms, two full baths, and over 2000 sqft! The home is in pristine condition and has a ton of upgrades to include granite counters, LVP flooring, stainless steel appliances, updated cabinets and showers, tons of storage, front and rear deck, fenced in yard and so much more! Inside includes two large family rooms, open kitchen, and an additional  bonus room.  Outside has tons of open space for gardening, relaxing, and an above ground pool! If you are looking for privacy and a rural setting, this one is surely to have everything you are looking for and more! This one will not disappoint, schedule your showing today!
